name: ALL-COLORS FRAME I CELL 001_1x1
description:
Hi, I'm Rubens AC Castro, Brazilian, business analyst and digital artist for over 20 years.
I created a digital panel of 155,520 x 87,480 pixels, with 300dpi of resolution 
and after that I divided it into 81 panels of 17,280 x 9,720 pixels, each with 81 images in Full HD, 1920 x 1080 x 300. 
All images are similar in shape and color, but none is the same. All images for sale will always be unique, exclusive.
From each frame of 81 images, I'll reserve one and make the other 80 available.
